<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$jeff-leo-18" href="/people/jeff-leo-18">佚名</a>，<strong title="简洁，直接，有效" class="zu-question-my-bio">简洁，直接，有效</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="242">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$jian-jian-de-wo" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/jian-jian-de-wo" class="zg-link" title="渐渐的我">渐渐的我</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zou-bu-dong-luo-li-ta" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zou-bu-dong-luo-li-ta" class="zg-link" title="走不动洛丽塔">走不动洛丽塔</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$hu-zhong-yu-39" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/hu-zhong-yu-39" class="zg-link" title="胡中钰">胡中钰</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2094647" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">试试看白色头带中间一条横向的黑色条纹，或者小字母。既可以和戴孝有足够区分度，效果没准比单色白色头带还好。<br>大概是这个方向，也可以试试白色打底上别的花饰。区分度和效果的最佳妥协点找到就好办了


</div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
